    • generateSqmExpression

      public final <T> SelfRenderingSqmFunction<T> generateSqmExpression(List<? extends SqmTypedNode<?>> arguments, ReturnableType<T> impliedResultType, QueryEngine queryEngine)
      Description copied from interface: SqmFunctionDescriptor
      Instantiate this template with the given arguments and expected return type. This produces a tree of SQM nodes representing a tree of function invocations. This allows a single HQL function to be defined in terms of other predefined (database independent) HQL functions, simplifying the task of writing HQL functions which are portable between databases.
      Specified by:
      generateSqmExpression in interface SqmFunctionDescriptor

      protected abstract <T> SelfRenderingSqmFunction<T> generateSqmFunctionExpression(List<? extends SqmTypedNode<?>> arguments, ReturnableType<T> impliedResultType, QueryEngine queryEngine)
